question_stem: Q4. Object “pred” is formed using the code in line 24. What is the length of “pred”?
question_stem_html: Q4. Object “pred” is formed using the code in line 24. What is the length of “pred”?

items.solution:
ANS: 1250
Explanation: The classifier here uses the train set as the original data set, knn(market[,X], market[,X], market[,Y], k=5)
And the test set is also the original data set, knn(market[,X], market[,X], market[,Y], k=5)
So, the prediction of outcome is for the test set with 1250 points.
